Basic little Kivy app to keep track of hours worked.

To get Kivy working, check out http://kivy.org/docs/installation/installation.html
Create a ve as per kivy installation page http://kivy.org/docs/installation/installation-linux.html

To run, enter the ve, cd to the dir with main in and run
python main.py

LCD Font found here
http://www.dafont.com/djb-get-digital.font

Background found here:
http://www.wallpaperel.com/aurora-earth-210695.html